<top>
<num> Number: 3401052-7
<title> One related direction in QR focuses on improving its precision by narrowing down a search query. In this case, the goal is to refine the query such that the refined alternative retrieves a more relevant subset of results. Approaches towards this task include learning rewritings based on past users’ query refinements [2, 31, 32] and applying pseudo-relevance feedback techniques [10, 29, 33, 45].

