<top>
<num> Number: 3401057-2
<title> To understand and capture student interests on MOOCs platforms, multiple efforts have been done, including course recommendation [13, 35], behavior prediction [20], user intentions understanding [34], etc. Among these efforts, recommendation system is applied by MOOCs provider to recommend courses to students.

