<num> Number: 3401103-7
<title> In [25] found SWD’s relevance ratings of webpages were highly correlated with their readability scores. They identified several visual and textual features such as line length, number of headings, and ratio of images to text, that impact SWDs’ readability and relevance judgements of webpages.

<desc> Description:

<narr> Narrative:

</top>

<top>
<num> Number: 3401103-8
<title> In [35] found using the "Reader View" mode in Firefox web browser, which simplifies a page’s visual structure, improved reading speed for SWD without reducing comprehension.

